PSE2011 -- Building Instructions
================================

- Install Python (python.org)
- put Antlr3 (antlr.org) in your java classpath
- do the same with SWT (eclipse.org/swt/)
- change directory into 'src', then run
    - python ./waf configure
    - python ./waf build -j 1
- change directory to ../bin
- Run via java -cp path/to/antlr.jar:path/to/swt.jar:./pse11.jar misc.MainClass
